Resistance.help: Armor plating gives Arachnobot Blasters good resistance to smashing and lethal damage. As machines, they are very resistant to psionic damage, but are vulnerable to EMP attacks. Arachnobots are excellent jumpers and are very fast.

Power_Jumping.help: Arachnobots can jump very high and travel very fast.
